# Ghostty Config Editing

Before suggesting any edits to a Ghostty config file, you MUST:

1. Fetch the Ghostty Configuration Manual: https://ghostty.org/docs/config/reference
2. Fetch the Ghostty Changelog: https://ghostty.org/docs/install/release-notes

Only suggest keys and values that are valid per the latest documentation. Do not use deprecated or removed keys. If a key's syntax has changed in a recent release, use the new syntax.
